commentTextItems.html: uses his feet and lofts it high and over the stands at long on, lovely strike to win the match. That's it Zimbabwe win by 7 wickets. The crowd are excited.

commentPostTextItems.html: The Zimbabwe players come out to shake hands with the Bangladesh players and the Umpires, the Zimbabwe players are doing a lap around the park, they have now taken the series 3-1 with one more match to play. Bangladesh did not have enough score on board to defend. Sibanda and Strydom put in a wonderful effort. In the end Matsikenyeri and Taylor finished it off in style. Utseya gets the man of the match for his wonderful spell of bowling, 25 runs for two wickets.
Thanks for being with us. This is Binoy George signing off. It is bye from all of us here at Cricinfo. Please join us again for the final ODI on August 6th.
